### 3. Load Order Services

```java
List<COrderService> orderServices = COrderServiceManager.load(order.getID());
```
- Retrieves all order services associated with the created order
- Typically one order service per screening request

---

### 4. Save Client References (`saveClientReferences`)

Saves various client-provided references as order properties:

#### 4.1 Host Instance Reference
```java
String sHostInstanceRef = request.getClientReference(EHostReference.HOST_INSTANCE_REF.getPropertyName());
if (sHostInstanceRef != null) {
    CInstanceDomain instanceDomain = CInstanceDomainFactory.search(sHostInstanceRef);
    COrderProperty.saveProperty(nOrderID, "HOST_INSTANCE_REF", instanceDomain.getDomainID(), true);
}
```

#### 4.2 Host Main Order Reference (as FlexField)
```java
String sHostMainOrderRef = request.getClientReference("HOST_MAIN_ORDER_REF");
if (!CStringUtils.isEmpty(sHostMainOrderRef)) {
    CFlexFieldDefinition flexFieldDefinition = 
        CFlexFieldDefinitionList.findDefinition(null, CCustomer.OBJECT_CLASS, "COMMON", true, "HostMainOrderReference");
    if (flexFieldDefinition != null) {
        CFlexField.create(null, flexFieldDefinition, COrder.OBJECT_CLASS, String.valueOf(nOrderID), sHostMainOrderRef);
    }
}
```

#### 4.3 Standard Order Properties
Saves the following references as order properties:
- `HOST_REQUESTOR_NAME` - Requestor's name
- `HOST_ORDER_SERVICE_REF` - Host system order service reference
- `HOST_ORDER_REF` - Host system order reference
- `HOST_DELAY_INFO_NOTE_RECIPIENTS` - Recipients for delay info notifications
- `HOST_DELAY_ACTION_NOTE_RECIPIENTS` - Recipients for delay action notifications

#### 4.4 Regulatory Properties
- `REGULATED_EMPLOYMENT_FLAG_7_YEARS`
- `REGULATION` - Regulation ID
- `REGULATION_FCA_ROLE_TYPE` - FCA role type
- `REGULATION_MAS_ROLE_TYPE` - MAS role type
- `REGULATION_ASIC_ROLE_TYPE` - ASIC role type
- `REGULATION_HK_ROLE_TYPE` - Hong Kong role type
- `REGULATION_MALAYSIA_ROLE_TYPE` - Malaysia role type
- `REGULATION_REGISTRATION_NUMBER`
- `REGULATION_COMPANY_NAME`
- `REGULATION_DEPARTMENT`
- `REGULATION_CONTACT_INFO`

#### 4.5 Verification & Configuration Properties
- `VS-814 SPELLING` - Spelling configuration
- `ALWAYS_FIRST_LAUNCH_TO_MANUAL_QUEUE` - Manual queue routing flag
- `ICOVER_API_ALWAYS_ROUTE_TO_MANUAL_QUEUE` - iCover API manual routing
- `SALARY_RESTRICTED` - Salary restriction flag
- `ALLOW_CONTACT_APPLICANT` - Permission to contact applicant
- `EDUCATION_VERIFY_HIGH_SCHOOL_AT_SOURCE` - High school verification flag

#### 4.6 Employment Verification Data Source Properties
- `EMPLOYMENT_EXPERIAN` - Experian data source flag
- `EMPLOYMENT_EXPERIAN_DATA_SET` - Experian dataset
- `EMPLOYMENT_EQUIFAX` - Equifax data source flag
- `EMPLOYMENT_EQUIFAX_DATA_SET` - Equifax dataset

